Speaker 2: It was 11, it was 11510 before that.

Speaker 1: I was at, I was at 2777 Park Avenue in Baldwin for 40 years.

Speaker 2: No, it updated the Maple app.

Speaker 1: Yeah, yeah, I updated the Maple app. I updated my credit card information.

Speaker 2: Okay. So, yeah, everything in there has been updated.

Speaker 1: So, I don't know why it's giving you the issue, unless were you trying to get the Viagra AGV?

Speaker 2: I was trying to get the new one, the new, the new, the new one.

Speaker 1: Okay, that's, yeah.

Speaker 2: What happened was it came up with the, it came up with the old one like they ordered years ago.

Speaker 1: Right, right.

Speaker 2: They won't let me get the new one.

Speaker 1: I know that, because that's the way the system's set up. It's not intentional, it's just the way the system is.

Speaker 2: I have to make the change on the phone, so I'll do that for you.

Speaker 1: Um, there's three options.

Speaker 2: Yeah, I'm going to go over that.

Speaker 1: Good.

Speaker 2: Yeah, so returning customer here, yeah, so 100 milligrams is what we would do for you again.

Speaker 1: So, 40 pills at $163.95, 25 at $113, or 10 at $63.95.

Speaker 2: And is that, that's the new, the new one to try out first, right?

Speaker 1: Yes, I am talking only about the new one.

Speaker 2: Okay, so let me ask you something. Let me try the, the small one to see how it works.

Speaker 1: And then if I like it, I'll get more for that.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Okay, that works.

Speaker 2: Um, so 10 of the 100 milligrams it is.

Speaker 1: And then, uh, I'm just going to, I know you said you just updated, but I'm going to confirm.

Speaker 2: The visa ending in 3497, right?

Speaker 1: I'm sorry?

Speaker 2: Yes, the new card is 3497.

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: Okay, perfect.

Speaker 1: That's great.

Speaker 2: Yes, I'm sorry.

Speaker 1: No, no, no, no, no problem.

Speaker 2: I just say we're all set on the order, so your prescription's going to update, then we'll mail it out.

Speaker 1: But if you have any questions or anything, let me know.

Speaker 2: All right, thank you so much.

Speaker 1: So, Scott, once I get the new order, can I, if I like it, then I can, I can get the, I can get the larger quantity, right?

Speaker 2: Oh, 100%, yes.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: And, but will I be able to do that on the phone, or I got to call you again, right?

Speaker 1: You can do it on the phone or call us, whatever you prefer.

Speaker 2: Okay, well, I select today, so it stopped me only because I never ordered this product before.

Speaker 1: Right, but now, now that I've made the change on our side, it should work for you on your side going forward.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: But if not, I'll call to one of your number.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Exactly.

Speaker 1: Five to seven days.

Speaker 2: Oh, that's great, sir.

Speaker 1: Thank you so much.

Speaker 2: You're welcome.

Speaker 1: You've been a big help.

Speaker 2: Of course.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.

Speaker 2: Bye-bye.
